### Test Customer Support Agent API

### Test simple greeting
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, I need help with my order

### Test order lookup - Ask about order 123
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

Can you look up my order 123?

### Test order lookup - Ask about order 456
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

What is the status of order 456?

### Test refund request for delivered order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

I would like to request a refund for order 456

### Test refund request for non-delivered order (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

Can I get a refund for order 123?

### Test refund for already refunded order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

I need a refund for order 456

### Test non-existent order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

Check order 999 for me

### Test complex conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/support/chat
Content-Type: text/plain

Hi, my name is John and I have a question about my recent purchase
